{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Device Orientation Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta es una <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">tecnología experimental</a></strong><br>Comprueba la <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Tabla de compabilidad de navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usarla en producción.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>El evento <code>DeviceMotionEvent</code> proporciona a los desarrolladores información acerca de la velocidad de los cambios en la posición y orientación del dispositivo.</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Aviso:</strong> Acualmente, Firefox and Chrome no manejan las corrdenadas de la misma forma. Tenga en cuenta esto cuando lo use.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.devicemotionevent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.DeviceMotionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Crea un nuevo <code>DeviceMotionEvent</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.acceleration_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>Objeto que nos proporciona la aceleración del dispositivo en los ejes X, Y y Z. La aceleración está expresada en <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s<sup>2</sup></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.accelerationincludinggravity_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>Objeto que nos proporciona la aceleración del dispositivo en los ejes X, Y y Z con el efecto de la gravedad. La aceleración está expresada en <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s<sup>2</sup></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.rotationrate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.rotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>Objeto que nos proporciona los cambios en la orientación del dispositivo en los ejes alpha, beta y gamma. La velocidad de rotación se expresa en grados por segundo</dd>\n <dt id=\"devicemotionevent.interval_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.interval</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n <dd>Número que representa el intervalo de tiempo, en milisegundos, en el que se obtienen los datos del dispositivo..</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'devicemotion'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>acceleration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">' m/s2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificación</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentario</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/#devicemotionevent\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DeviceOrientation Event Specification<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'DeviceMotionEvent' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">Editor's Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compativilidad con los navegadores","id":"compativilidad_con_los_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events/Detecting_device_orientation\" title=\"/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Detecting_device_orientation\">Detecting device orientation</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en/DOM/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\" title=\"Orientation and motion data explained\">Orientation and motion data explained</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compativilidad con los navegadores","id":"compativilidad_con_los_navegadores"},{"text":